{
  "stem": "11611.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was a hiatus, quiet period during the Cold War, and it was the custom during quiet periods of the Cold War to heat them up-- because you had to have a constant anti-communist public opinion in the United States.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was necessary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Normally in this espionage center, which was Vienna, I mean, where about 1/3 third of the total population engaged in nothing but spying, you would try people before court martials, they would get a two-month sentence and that was it.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they decided to make a showcase trial out of Werber.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they brought him here and put him on trial.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got a call from the jail.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know anything about local criminal practice, and so I went down to the jail to talk to him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There are all kinds of ways of handling these things where you don't go to the jail and talk to them-- but I didn't know any of the-- any of the ropes.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was a tax lawyer by this time, through Charlie Lyons, who had become assistant attorney general of the tax division.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was working for Randolph Paul, who was a famous tax lawyer, and who was involved in some libel case as a lawyer, defending Wechsler of Walter Winchell case.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was very awkward to, in any way, represent anybody charged with anything communist.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went down to see Werber, and I said, what are the charges?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What's it all about?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, oh, I'm innocent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he started to give me a story which was concocted, which was transparently false.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Among other things, he claimed he did some work for Jewish agencies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was strictly-- he was Jewish, but he wasn't connected with anything Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was connected with the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
